<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Weight Gain Plan (25-40 Overweight)</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Weight Gain Plan (25-40 Overweight)</h1>

        <h2>Diet Plan (Weekly Variation)</h2>
        <table border="1">
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Breakfast</th>
                <th>Lunch</th>
                <th>Snacks</th>
                <th>Dinner</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Low-fat yogurt, mixed berries, and a handful of almonds</td>
                <td>Grilled fish, steamed greens, and quinoa</td>
                <td>Protein shake and walnuts</td>
                <td>Stir-fried tofu with vegetables and brown rice</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>Oatmeal with flaxseeds and banana</td>
                <td>Chicken breast with quinoa and steamed vegetables</td>
                <td>Carrot sticks with hummus</td>
                <td>Baked salmon with roasted sweet potatoes</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Scrambled eggs with spinach and whole wheat toast</td>
                <td>Grilled shrimp with brown rice and sautéed greens</td>
                <td>Handful of cashews and a green smoothie</td>
                <td>Stir-fried tofu with bell peppers and quinoa</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Chia seed pudding with walnuts and blueberries</td>
                <td>Turkey and avocado wrap with mixed greens</td>
                <td>Greek yogurt with honey and almonds</td>
                <td>Grilled chicken with roasted vegetables</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>Boiled eggs with whole wheat toast and green tea</td>
                <td>Salmon with lentils and steamed broccoli</td>
                <td>Apple slices with peanut butter</td>
                <td>Vegetable stir-fry with tofu and quinoa</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Protein smoothie (banana, almond milk, protein powder)</td>
                <td>Lean beef stir-fry with brown rice</td>
                <td>Handful of sunflower seeds and a protein shake</td>
                <td>Grilled fish with asparagus and mashed cauliflower</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Avocado toast with poached eggs</td>
                <td>Quinoa salad with chickpeas and grilled chicken</td>
                <td>Cottage cheese with flaxseeds</td>
                <td>Baked turkey breast with roasted Brussels sprouts</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <h2>Gym Routine (Fat Burning & Muscle Building)</h2>
        <table border="1">
            <tr>
                <th>Day</th>
                <th>Workout</th>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Monday</td>
                <td>Strength Training (Upper Body: Bench press, rows, push-ups, shoulder press)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Tuesday</td>
                <td>HIIT Cardio (Jump squats, burpees, battle ropes, sprints - 30 mins)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Wednesday</td>
                <td>Strength Training (Lower Body: Squats, lunges, deadlifts, calf raises)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Thursday</td>
                <td>Moderate Cardio & Core (Cycling, rowing, planks, Russian twists)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Friday</td>
                <td>HIIT & Functional Fitness (Kettlebells, sled push, medicine ball slams)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Saturday</td>
                <td>Active Recovery (Yoga, hiking, or swimming)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>Sunday</td>
                <td>Rest Day</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
